OL,3,CFirst to be charged with causing
OL,4,Cinjury by dangerous driving is jailed
OL,6,FThe first person to be charged with
OL,7,Fcausing a serious injury by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving in Guernsey has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor four months.
OL,11,F43 year old Matthew Luscombe was
OL,12,Fbehind the wheel when his car crashed
OL,13,Finto other vehicles on Amherst Road at
OL,14,FBeau Sejour, at around 4.30pm in
OL,15,FNovember.
OL,17,FThe other driver spent two nights in
OL,18,Fintensive care after suffering serious
OL,19,Finjuries.
