OL,6,FLuscombe failed a roadside breath
OL,7,Ftest, and was found to be double the
OL,8,Flegal drink drive limit.
OL,10,FLuscombe pleaded guilty to drink
OL,11,Fdriving and causing serious injury by
OL,12,Fdangerous driving. As well as his jail
OL,13,Fsentence, he was banned from driving
OL,14,Ffor four years at Guernsey's
OL,15,FMagistrates Court.
