OL,6,FThe new road traffic laws came into
OL,7,Faffect in March 2025. It included a
OL,8,Fmore detailed explanation of what
OL,9,Fconstitutes driving dangerously and
OL,10,Falso clarifies the meaning of driving
OL,11,Fwithout due care and attention, and
OL,12,Fdriving without reasonable
OL,13,Fconsideration for others.
OL,15,FUnder the new law, 'dangerous'
OL,16,Freferred to the "danger either of
OL,17,Finjury to any person or of serious
OL,18,Fdamage to property" caused by the
OL,19,Findividual's driving.
